  Translator: Burton Watson
By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 10
  Paragraph: 5
Title: Rifling Trunks
---
Chih replied, "How could he get anywhere if he didn't have a Way?
Making shrewd guesses as to how much booty is stashed away in the room
is sageliness; being the first one in is bravery; being the last one
out is righteousness; knowing whether the job can be pulled off or not
is wisdom; dividing up the loot fairly is benevolence. No one in the
world ever succeeded in becoming a great thief if he didn't have all
five!"
